```plantuml
@startuml terrenjpeterson_javawatch
actor User
participant RaspberryPi
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "Lambda (checkImage.py)" as LambdaCheckImage
participant "Amazon Rekognition" as Rekognition
participant "Lambda (labelCheck.js)" as LambdaLabelCheck
participant "Amazon DRS" as DRS
participant "Website" as Website

User -> RaspberryPi: Triggers photo capture
RaspberryPi -> S3: Uploads timestamped image
S3 -> LambdaCheckImage: Triggers on new image
LambdaCheckImage -> Rekognition: detect_labels(image)
Rekognition --> LambdaCheckImage: Returns labels
LambdaCheckImage -> LambdaLabelCheck: Process labels (check for "Bean")
LambdaLabelCheck --> LambdaCheckImage: Bean presence confirmed
LambdaCheckImage -> DRS: Place order (if low bean level)
DRS --> Website: Order confirmation
Website --> User: Displays order status
@enduml
```